hene. Our results suggest this\nemerging class of exotic quantum materials can be harnessed for photo detection\nwith high sensitivity and high speed (~145 GHz) in challenging\nmiddle/far-infrared and THz range.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 2 Sep 2016 23:56:03 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-01-20"}
